content.title: Duba samun damar dubawa
content.howToUseTooltip:
Da ke ƙasa akwai halaye na alamar wannan kumburin don za a zaɓi ayyukan, kamar danna, cikawa a rubutu, da sauransu.

Ana iya kwantar da ƙimar sifa a cikin shafin App. Idan ka hadu da kwafin, da fatan za a share wasu mahimmin mahimmin mahimmin bayani don sanin daidaituwa.

Kalmar Red tana nuna cewa ana maimaita ƙimar ƙimar sifa, wata kalma kore tana nuna cewa ƙimar sifa ta musamman ne a cikin binciken shafi na yanzu, kuma kalmar baƙar fata tana nuna cewa babu maimaitawa.
content.moreNodes: Ga abin da ake fadada shi.
